Note to developers: be sure that you use etc/git/hook/pre-commit as your pre-commit hook.

Recommended git config values (you may wish to add --global to some of them):

git config user.name <Your name in AUTHORS file (add one if needed)>
git config user.email <Your e-mail in AUTHORS file>
git config core.autocrlf auto
git config rerere.enabled true
git config color.ui auto
